data.description: Beautiful Single Story 4-2-2 Home backing to greenbelt with mature trees, Spacious open concept. Living,Dining & Kitchen with Island, Quartz Countertops,Stainles Steel Appliances & Walk In Pantry.Larger Primary Bedroom with 5 ft over sized Shower & Walk In Closet.Tiled Entry,Hall,Living,Dining,Kitchen & wet areas plus Home is Connected Smart Home Technology.Covered back Patio,6 ft fenced Backyard, full Sprinkler System.Close to I-35W & HWY 67*Minutes from Alvarado, Burleson, Cleburne & Downtown Ft Worth Property is equipped with solar panel which are financed through Sonova and buyer must assume the Loan.
